==English==
===Noun===
'''caricature'''
#a [[pictorial]] [[representation]] of someone in which [[distinguishing]] [[feature]]s are [[exaggerated]] for [[comic]] [[effect]]
#a [[grotesque]] [[misrepresentation]]
===Transitive verb===
'''to caricature'''
#to [[represent]] someone in an exaggerated or [[distorted]] manner
